---
title: Beef Bulgogi Lettuce Wraps with Rice & Spicy Pickles
description: The star of this fresh spin on Korean tacos is juicy ground beef sizzled to savory-sweet perfection in bulgogi sauce (one of our favorite ways to pack in that umami-rich sesame-soy flavor we love). You’ll sprinkle with crackly, nutty sesame seeds and serve it in crisp lettuce cups along with fluffy rice and tangy-spicy pickled cucumbers that add a hit of refreshing heat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663a6e71be3ee05a950c3885-20e588bd.jpeg
